{2000}{}{Who let you in here?@@I don't receive visitors. How did you get in here?}
{2010}{}{Excuse me, I must have gotten the wrong door. [Leave]}
{2020}{}{Who are you?}
{2030}{}{General, I want to prove my loyalty to NCR. Is there anything I can do for the Republic?}
{2040}{}{General, I want to prove my loyalty to NCR. Is there anything I can do for the Republic?}
{2050}{}{General, I delivered the documents to Brotherhood of Steel.}
{2060}{}{General, I have here the official response of Brotherhood Paladins to your protest.}
{3000}{}{If you don't know who I am, you shouldn't be here. Guards, arrest this citizen.}
{3010}{}{How about ME arresting YOUR ass?! [Attack]}
{3020}{}{No need for that, I'm already leaving. [Leave]}
{4000}{}{You should get out at once or you'll be arrested.}
{4010}{}{Fine, bye. [Leave]}
{5000}{}{I've heard a lot of good stuff about you. People say you're trustworthy. Well, I have a mission for you.}
{5010}{}{A combat mission, I hope?}
{6000}{}{A diplomatic mission. You must get a package of documents to San Francisco and hand it to Brotherhood of Steel paladins.}
{6010}{}{Brotherhood?}
{7000}{}{Brotherhood of Steel. You know who they are, right?}
{7010}{}{Of course. What's in the package?}
{8000}{}{Very important documents. To put it concisely, it's an official NCR protest to Brotherhood expansion to Republic controlled territory. }
{8010}{}{What are you talking about?}
{9000}{}{Are you going to discuss the mission or follow the given order?}
{9010}{}{I need time to make up my mind. [Leave]}
{9020}{}{I'm sorry, sir. I'll deliver the package without asking unnecessary questions.}
{10000}{}{Excellent. These are the documents you must deliver to paladins. [Gives you the package] Take as much care of it as of your own life. }
{10010}{}{Yes, sir. Is it all I have to do?}
{11000}{}{Hand the protest. Wait for their reaction and receive the response, which should be delivered to me personally. That is all.}
{11010}{}{Understood, General, sir. Permission to leave? }
{12000}{}{Dismissed.}
{13000}{}{[Raises his eyebrow in amazement] What? You managed to do it? They listened to you?! Incredible! Give it to me.}
{13010}{}{[Hand the briefcase with the documents]}
{14000}{}{[Shaiman opens the briefcase, takes the document and starts to read. The more he reads, the more red in the face he becomes] The bastards! You asked for it. I won't leave this outrage unanswered. [Raises his eyes] Thank you for your service. You've done a lot for the Republic. You may be free.}
{14010}{}{Goodbye. [Leave]}
{14020}{}{Maybe I could do anything else for the Republic?}
{15000}{}{What was their reaction to the protest?}
{15010}{}{They didn't even read it... Of course there was no official response...}
{16000}{}{Revolting, @pname@! I thought better of you. }
{16010}{}{Nobody listened to me...}
{17000}{}{Dismissed.}
{18000}{}{I don't have any work for you. Find Santiago, he needs a reliable man. I'll tell him you can be trusted.}
{18010}{}{I'll do that, thank you, sir. [Leave]}
{19000}{}{Huh? What's this delegation? What's the matter? I'm listening.}
{19010}{}{Vault City Guard representatives plenipotentiary reporting, sir.}
{20000}{}{You don't say so. And what the hell do Vault City Guard representatives plenipotentiary need in my office?}
{20010}{}{First of all, sir, let me assure you of the great respect for you from our administration -  head of the city and guard commander. Our commander personally asked to covey to you that your military operations set an example of tactical solutions and strategic thinking…}
{20020}{}{General, we have something to talk about. We need your assistance. And you could very well use ours.}
{21000}{}{Huh? He really thinks so? Hmm… all right. So what?}
{21010}{}{Secondly, this very respect made him send this delegation with a plea for help. Notwithstanding the fact that Brotherhood of Steel for instance offers us…}
{22000}{}{Everybody needs my help. Huh. In what way are you different from anyone else? It's fun to hear you ask for my help and then mumble something about your own. Be clearer, you.}
{22010}{}{I think I am clear enough. We want military aid from you. Mutant aggression has been getting more and more intense lately…}
{22020}{}{I'm sorry, general. I'll try to be more concise. The city administration is under great impression of your military operations against mutants.}
{23000}{}{Brotherhood? I wouldn't hear of them! They are prying into your affairs too?}
{23010}{}{Yes, general, sir. Brotherhood is trying to poke its nose into our business. But our commander is sure there are no strategists of your scale in the Brotherhood, sir. That's why he denied them. And that's why we are here. We need your help, general.}
{24000}{}{Well, I don't give a damn about what's been getting more intense…}
{24010}{}{Don't burn the bridges, general, might want to use them someday…}
{25000}{}{Hmm, yeah. The mutants are a nuisance. Remnants of Master's army cannot be brushed aside.}
{25010}{}{Agreed, sir. Same thing's going on with us, sir. The mutants are getting more and more numerous. Your experience in dealing with them would be most invaluable.}
{26000}{}{Looks like your commander is a smart man. Good thing there still are some sensible people in the wasteland… What assistance particularly do you have in mind?}
{26010}{}{In case of massive mutant assault on the city we want your troops to move out to assist us, sir. We will of course provide them with ammunition and medical supplies…}
{27000}{}{Who are you to fucking lecture me? I repeat. I. DON'T. GIVE. A. DAMN. Now get out of here!}
{27010}{}{I'll be back. [Leave]}
{28000}{}{Yeah, I sure got enough experience to fill three @sex@|lads||girls| like you. What is it that you want exactly?}
{28010}{}{In case of massive mutant assault on the city we want your troops to move out to assist us, sir. We will of course provide them with ammunition and medical supplies…}
